Interface ILevel3Controller

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ILevel1Controller, ILevel2Controller
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlphaServer, DesignManager, Module

    public interface ILevel3Controller
extends ILevel2Controller
    A level 3 controller is a level 2 controller that can also return references. The default methods of this interface need not to be overwritten.
